          <msContents>
            <summary>Manuscript is a kind of manual of rites and contains prayers for use during rites of purification, getting rid of obstacles, and similar rites, on an auspicious day (puṇyāha); it is especially used for purifying children shortly after birth.</summary>
            <textLang mainLang="san">In Sanskrit</textLang>
            <msItem>
