              </respStmt>
              <colophon>Colophon: mitī caitraśuddha 9 bhomavāsare puṣyadivasanakṣe śake 1757 parābhavanāmasaṃvatsare pustakavāsudevātmajaparśarāmabhaṭṭabhāvyena likhitaṃ // (f. 6r).</colophon>
